Titolo: Everest Ascent

Anno: 1983

Descrizione: Everest Ascent is a text and graphics adventure game for the ZX Spectrum and Commodore 64 computers. It was published by Richard Shepherd Software in 1984.  The goal of the game is to reach the top of Mount Everest in 20 days.  Players must allocate their limited funds to keep their sherpas well fed and supplied in order to reach the summit.